-- Ambac trading halted on NYSE
-- 
-- Wed Mar 5, 2008 12:15pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/03/05/us-ambac-halt-idUSWEN434520080305

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Trading in Ambac Financial Group Inc ABK.N, the bond insurer, was halted around midday Wednesday on the New York Stock Exchange. 

 No further information was immediately available. Ambac shares were trading up 63 cents, or 5.9 percent, at $11.35 prior to the halt. Shares of MBIA Inc ( MBI.N ), another bond insurer, were up $1.22, or 9.4 percent, at $14.20. Trading in MBIA shares was not halted.